  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Customer Outreach Rep",
  "description": "<h2>🚀 Company Overview / Why Vision Organisation</h2><p>Vision Organisation is a people-focused sales & marketing firm that works with leading brands to bring campaigns to life.<br />We believe the best way to learn is <strong>on the ground</strong> — through real conversations, real experiences, and real growth.</p><p>If you enjoy learning by doing and growing with a team, you’ll fit right in.</p><h2>🎯 Job Summary</h2><p>As part of our team, you’ll engage customers through live, on-ground campaigns, represent client brands, and build strong communication and sales skills through hands-on experience.<br />This is an active, people-facing role designed for those who enjoy interaction and practical learning.</p><h2>🔥 What You’ll Be Doing</h2><ul><li><p>👋 Start friendly, face-to-face conversations with customers</p></li><li><p>🎤 Represent client brands clearly and confidently at events, roadshows, and outreach activities</p></li><li><p>🤝 Build rapport and deliver brand messages in a positive, engaging way</p></li><li><p>📈 Apply sales and communication skills through real-world interactions</p></li><li><p>👥 Work closely with teammates to support campaign goals and shared success</p></li></ul><h2>🌟 What We’re Looking For</h2><ul><li><p>Comfortable interacting with people in different settings</p></li><li><p>Willing to learn, take initiative, and try new things</p></li><li><p>Reliable, adaptable, and able to work well in a team</p></li><li><p>Enjoys active, on-the-ground, full-time work</p></li></ul><h2>🎓 What You’ll Get</h2><ul><li><p>🤝 Hands-on training, guidance, and team support</p></li><li><p>📚 Practical experience in customer engagement and sales</p></li><li><p>📈 Performance-based growth and skill development</p></li><li><p>🌍 Opportunities to work on different campaigns and locations</p></li></ul><h2>📩 How to Apply</h2><p>If you’d like to gain real-world experience in customer engagement and sales, we’d love to hear from you.</p><p>📱 <strong>WhatsApp:</strong> 9820 2507<br />💬 <strong>Telegram:</strong> @nitsualim</p>",
